    "media:imagetext": "HUNULULU LUS ANGELES SAN FRANCISCO SEATILE\nWho's the man\nbehind the planning?\nHe knows about reservations, ex-\ncursion fares, inclusive tours, SAS\nspecial services, hotel accommo-\ndation, extra-city plans, passports\nand currencies. He's an expert.\nHe's your SAS-appointed travel\nagent. His job is to carry the burden\nof your travel planning, whether for\nbusiness, study or pleasure. His\nexpert advice and services can\nsave you a lot of time and money.\nIt makes good travel sense to take\nadvantage of them - especially. as\nhis advice is free.\nTravel advice is\nfreely, expertly given\nby your SAS-appointed\ntravel agent.\nntercontinenta network ol\nSAS and associate airlines\nConnecting routes\nFOR COMPLETE EUROPEAN NETWORK\nSEE PRECEDING PAGE",
